<p>Attached please find written comments in response to the recommendations made to the NAPA Council from the IOM Advanced Dementia meetings. I was pleased to be an observer at the meetings on behalf of AFTD and the individuals with FTD and their families whom we represent.</p>
<p>Thank you for your efforts and those of all the council members.</p>
