<li>Commission on Long-Term Care, <em>Report to the Congress 5</em> (September 30, 2013) available at <a href="http://ltccommission.lmp01.lucidus.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Commission-on-Long-Term-Care-Final-Report-9-26-13.pdf">http://ltccommission.lmp01.lucidus.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Commission-on-Long-Term-Care-Final-Report-9-26-13.pdf</a>.</li>
